data.description: Attention Investors & Contractors......First time on the market in 53 years!  Charming fixer (in livable condition) in a prime  location within walking distance to all the shops & restaurants on El Paseo Dr. Huge lot of almost 14,000 square feet. Pool, mountain views and mature vegetation. New roof in 2018.  One of two AC units replaced in 2018. Remodeled properties in this area have sold well above 1.5 million.  Looking for cash buyers for a quick close.   Property sold as-is.
